  "2172980": {
    "name": "Fading Light VR: Antiworld",
    "steam_appid": 2172980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/b72ab883a8e375dd3d74905653c637fd.webp?t=1733125979\" width=607 height=49 /></span>  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/18e9731aaeba96978f8d8a06c87a04bd.webp?t=1733125979\" width=607 height=49 /></span><br><strong>隔离区：辐岛 · 第一章</strong> 是由独立游戏团队SUPLIFE开发的第一视角恐怖探险游戏，故事时间背景设定在战后的核灾难世界，玩家将扮演资深核能工程师，在灾后的反物质世界里探索未知，躲避潜伏在阴暗中的威胁，并安全逃离辐岛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/90775c6a8e4dc95f0f4239139eaf9492.webp?t=1733125979\" width=607 height=49 /></span><br>三战中，核电站被敌机轰炸造成了严重的核泄露。你从昏迷中苏醒，发现自己被困在诡异的反物质时空，在午夜12点到次晨6点间无限循环。为了生存下去，你必须不断战斗。但小心，在这个神秘的暗夜空间里，你永远不知道什么正在暗中等待着你...  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/3899ea81b1cce629a9ac9018ef6313b0.poster.avif?t=1733125979\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/3899ea81b1cce629a9ac9018ef6313b0.webm?t=1733125979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/3899ea81b1cce629a9ac9018ef6313b0.mp4?t=1733125979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/513cb6c16d66c44db6745b3ef375fd06.webp?t=1733125979\" width=607 height=49 /></span><br>神秘的房间，若隐若现的血迹，闹鬼的电视，黑暗中的声音... 隔离区：辐岛从场景，音效到玩法全方位为恐怖游戏玩家创造沉浸式恐怖体验，致力让玩家身临其境，在恐惧与未知中开启毛骨悚然的恐怖之旅。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/6ddb3a6c605c1d2ea50a5bf5edc5060e.poster.avif?t=1733125979\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/6ddb3a6c605c1d2ea50a5bf5edc5060e.webm?t=1733125979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/6ddb3a6c605c1d2ea50a5bf5edc5060e.mp4?t=1733125979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/eb8fc35ff333369569bda1b646326f36.webp?t=1733125979\" width=607 height=49 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>探索:   你伴随着一阵头晕目眩，墙上报纸中敌军空袭的消息，似乎把你拉回核电站爆炸时的冲击波袭来的瞬间。究竟发生了什么？你又如何被卷入无人时空？在这危机四伏的黑暗空间，你将在恐惧与疑惑中开启令人毛骨悚然的未知之旅。<br>    </li><li>敌人:  诡异的怪物彷佛无处不在，它不断折磨你的意志，企图阻挠你逃出辐岛。面对恐怖的敌人，你将意识到自己的微弱。你必须一边躲避它的追击，一边想方设法逃出生天，这将是一场智与勇的对决。<br>    </li><li>收集:  通过吸取收集匹配公寓内相同物件产生的正反物质能量为手电筒蓄电，撑到你能逃出房间的那一刻。幸好，作为核能工程师，你有专业的设备帮助你吸收这些神奇的物质。战略，经验和对黑暗环境的认知将是你能否征服强敌的关键。<br>    </li><li>生存:  神秘而邪恶的声音如影随形，唯有手中微弱的光源貌似能阻止它的靠近。随着时间的流逝，光源越来越暗，如何积攒光能，为手电筒蓄能，将是你在这个黑暗的房间独自生存最重要的考验。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/0e6d492e6b665c0385b1b1c4b00e82a1.poster.avif?t=1733125979\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/0e6d492e6b665c0385b1b1c4b00e82a1.webm?t=1733125979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172980/extras/0e6d492e6b665c0385b1b1c4b00e82a1.mp4?t=1733125979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
